12. Bd2 Ba7 { Making room for the c6-knight to jump to d4. } 13. O-O Nd4 14.
Nc3 O-O
{ The following sequence has been played in a game Deac-Palac @@StartBracket@@2021@@EndBracket@@: }
15. Kh1 b5 16. Be2 c6 17. a4 h6 18. f4
