{ Covering the d-file before playing ...b6 and ...Bb7, is just fine for Black. }
14. b3 { Now we may decide to change our plan and go for: } 14... Ne4
{ Followed by ...Bf5, ...Rd7, ...Rad8, with a position that starts to be more pleasant to play as Black. }
