15... Rxd3 16. Nc4 Be6 17. Nb6 Ra7 { Simply protecting the b7-pawn. } 18. Nc5
Rd2
{ Black has nothing to worry about here. The likely outcome of the game is a massive pieces/pawns exchange. }
