Bc3 { Critical.   Here  19.Be3  wouldn't help due to  19...b6  . } 19... Rxa7
20. Bxg7 Re8 21. Bh6 f6
{ The position is just unclear. Black's next moves are likely to be ...Bf5, ...Be4, while the a7-rook will be activated with ...Ra6 or ...b6. }
