19. O-O Nxe4 20. Nxe4 Bc6 21. Bxb4 Qxd3 22. exd3 axb4 23. Rfd1 Rfd8
{ Offers Black full compensation due to the weakness of the d3-pawn and the powerful c6-bishop. }
