16. Bd2 exd3 17. exd3 Bg4
{ It's always good to provoke f2-f3, closing the g2-bishop. } 18. f3 Bf5 19. d4
Bd3 20. Rf2 Rfe8 { Black is very comfortable and dominates the light squares. }
21. c4 Qa6 { Just loses as ...Bxc2 and ...Nxd4 is coming. } *

