{ Was more than comfortable for Black in the game Navara,D @@StartBracket@@2717@@EndBracket@@-Huschenbeth,N @@StartBracket@@2624@@EndBracket@@ Czech Republic 2019, 1-0 @@StartBracket@@37@@EndBracket@@, although in the end Black lost. Black will castle next and has really nothing to worry about. }
