Qc2 { 13.Qxd4??  Be5  wins a piece. } 13... dxe3 14. dxe3 O-O-O
{ White is underdeveloped and Black's king is absolutely safe on the queenside. Would both players try to attack with opposite castles, Black is likely to be quicker, bringing his queen to h5 to simply pushing his h-pawn. }
